						<summary>

						<p>A broken slab set up near the house of the karaṅam.</p>						

						<p>1365 A.D.</p>						

						<p>It is dated Śaka 1277, Plavanga, Kārttika śu. 5, Friday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to register the sale of land by certain Prōlajiyya probably at Animela. It mentions <hi rend="italic">vudida paḍagādaṇu.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
